{"tid":732694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：香港不願見到中美貿易戰","createTime":"2018-07-07T06:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T08:21:11.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"88c715ab1a09f47bb4f5f20e1c2fa57de2467321","tid":732694,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/林鄭月娥-香港不願見到中美貿戰-081229176.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8D%E9%A1%98%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%88%B0-081229176.html&d=zrTRZ2mwaJxZQo0%2B%2FKHujcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c559b520\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/林鄭月娥-香港不願見到中美貿戰-081229176.html</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，如果中國和美國打貿易戰，香港肯定會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出訪法國期間，接受鳳凰衛視專訪時說，香港是全球第七大的貿易經濟體，很多貨物都是經香港，由內地轉口到美國，或者由美國轉口到內地，香港不願意見到中美打貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，香港是世界貿易組織的成員，一向非常重視自由貿易，希望其他國家都能夠明白全球經濟發展趨勢，是走向開放，並非走向封閉。"},{"pid":"b4e6e732afa8f7fb6f70d0b073a77ef14eb8975e","tid":732694,"uid":52271,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"呢D外交野幾時到你俾意見"},{"pid":"c599ed7144fea36c1aa0fbe8529546c1b3e71b14","tid":732694,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:37:09.000Z","msg":"感該叫係&quot;內地美國貿易戰&quot;"},{"pid":"a84ea22b0b2283c97abf96cdad62f384e86318e6","tid":732694,"uid":10890,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"區區一個市長 幾時輪到你出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n努力支那中國製造2025好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{